Package io.github.jnodorp.jiffybox.internal

Class DefaultMonitoringCheckBuilderFactory

java.lang.Object
io.github.jnodorp.jiffybox.internal.DefaultMonitoringCheckBuilderFactory
All Implemented Interfaces:
MonitoringCheckBuilderFactory
public class DefaultMonitoringCheckBuilderFactory extends Object implements MonitoringCheckBuilderFactory
This class is used to create monitoring check builder of different types. Use any of the methods you need and get the builder.
